<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;

        }
        .background-image {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: url('https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/hand-painted-watercolor-abstract-watercolor-background_23-2149012404.jpg'); 
            background-size: cover; /* Apply the blur effect, you can adjust the amount (5px) as needed */
            z-index: -1; /* Place it behind other content */
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
            background-image: url('https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/hand-painted-watercolor-abstract-watercolor-background_23-2149012404.jpg');
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin: 0;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .buttons {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        a {
            display: block;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #38383875;
            background-image: linear-gradient(45deg,#f06bd5cc, #5cd3f4b1 );
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #8b0f0f;
            border-color: #55555574;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="background-image"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to Blood Zone</h1>
        <p>Please sign in or sign up to donate  and make lives colourful.</p>
        <div class="buttons">
            <a href="register" class="login-button">Sign up</a>
            <a href="login" class="login-button">Sign in</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>